## tool-limits: limit_list and limit_set tool definitions

### limit_list() → str
List all configurable depth and iteration limits with their current values and descriptions.
Valid keys include: max_at_llm_depth, max_agent_call_depth.
Read-only. Requires read gate approval (controlled by !limit_list_gate_read, default: gated).

### limit_set(key: str, value: int) → str
Update a configurable depth or iteration limit and persist it to llm-models.json.
Changes take effect after agent restart.
Valid keys: max_at_llm_depth, max_agent_call_depth.
Requires write gate approval (controlled by !limit_set_gate_write, default: gated).
